msgid ""
"How to use `firewalld` to restrict or allow incoming and outgoing connections"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../src/docs/guides/security/firewalld-beginners.md:26
msgid ""
"How to allow only people from certain IP addresses or places to log into "
"your machine remotely"
msgstr ""

